com.vector.cfg.automation.scripting.base

Interface INotExecutableReasonBuilder


  • @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public interface INotExecutableReasonBuilder
    INotExecutableReasonBuilder is used to set information for the user, why a certain IScriptTask is currently not executable.

    (c) Copyright Vctr Informatik GmbH. All Rights Reserved.

    IScriptTask

void addReason(java.lang.String message)
        Adds a reason, why the IScriptTask is not executable.

        The reason is display the the user, when the IScriptTask shall be called, but is not executable
